d=\"ec5493c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Changer durablement la vie des femmes implique aussi de faire \u00e9voluer les mentalit\u00e9s, les repr\u00e9sentations et les comportements. La Fondation des Femmes mobilise la soci\u00e9t\u00e9 enti\u00e8re \u2013 citoyen\u00b7nes, m\u00e9dias, institutions, entreprises, lieux culturels \u2013 gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 des campagnes de sensibilisation, des \u00e9v\u00e9nements f\u00e9d\u00e9rateurs, des formations et des contenus engag\u00e9s, pour faire de l\u2019\u00e9galit\u00e9 une cause partag\u00e9e par toutes et tous.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6b85a84 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6b85a84\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"688\" src=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/hero-mobiliser-1024x881.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-16069\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/hero-mobiliser-1024x881.webp 1024w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/hero-mobiliser-300x258.webp 300w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/hero-mobiliser-768x661.webp 768w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/hero-mobiliser.webp 1198w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9bb20c6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9bb20c6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ba587f4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"ba587f4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b8aad1b elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b8aad1b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Des <span class=\"highlight-jaune\">campagnes<\/span> qui marquent les esprits<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fb7017e elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fb7017e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Chaque ann\u00e9e, la Fondation des Femmes lance des campagnes de communication fortes autour \u2028du 8 mars (Journ\u00e9e internationale des droits des femmes) et du 25 novembre (Journ\u00e9e internationale pour l\u2019\u00e9limination des violences faites aux femmes), pour sensibiliser le grand public et collecter \u2028des fonds pour les associations.\u200b<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5ed19ec e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"5ed19ec\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0e7ee20 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"0e7ee20\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e40d5d2 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"e40d5d2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"741\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/campagne-coups-d-arret-741x1024.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-16060\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/campagne-coups-d-arret-741x1024.webp 741w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/campagne-coups-d-arret-217x300.webp 217w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/campagne-coups-d-arret-768x1062.webp 768w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/campagne-coups-d-arret.webp 1040w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 741px) 100vw, 741px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ab1c3a5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"ab1c3a5\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6925af0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6925af0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5ea6700 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5ea6700\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Tous les coups<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6a4bd49 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6a4bd49\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">25 novembre 2025<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-65835ce elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"65835ce\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Une campagne de sensibilisation centr\u00e9e sur les violences conjugales et les m\u00e9canismes d\u2019emprise, pour rappeler que tous les coups ne sont pas visibles et que la violence ne se limite pas aux coups physiques. Elle invite chacune et chacun \u00e0 ne plus minimiser ces violences et \u00e0 soutenir les associations qui accompagnent les victimes.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b645bc7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"b645bc7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Voir la campagne<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c79d861 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c79d861\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-12ac282 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"12ac282\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-efea5ae e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"efea5ae\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-93e02e9 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"93e02e9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-20f524b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"20f524b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">L\u2019\u00e9vidence reste un combat<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0afba90 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0afba90\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">8 mars 2025<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8353fcb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8353fcb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Cette campagne rappelle que ce qui devrait \u00eatre une \u00e9vidence \u2013 l\u2019\u00e9galit\u00e9, la libert\u00e9, le respect du corps des femmes, l\u2019acc\u00e8s \u00e0 la sant\u00e9 ou \u00e0 la justice \u2013 reste encore, en 2025, l\u2019objet de combats quotidiens. En confrontant des \u00ab \u00e9vidences \u00bb affich\u00e9es \u00e0 la r\u00e9alit\u00e9 des chiffres, la campagne montre que rien n\u2019est acquis et que l\u2019engagement de toutes et tous reste indispensable.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bf320f7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"bf320f7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"#\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Voir la campagne<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n