lic autour de la lutte contre les violences faites aux femmes. Devant pr\u00e8s de 5 000 personnes et des millions de t\u00e9l\u00e9spectateurs lors de la diffusion sur TMC, le show a permis de sensibiliser largement et de collecter des fonds suppl\u00e9mentaires pour les associations.\u200b<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div id=\"e-n-tab-content-1442899643\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"e-n-tab-title-1442899643\" data-tab-index=\"3\" style=\"--n-tabs-title-order: 3;\" class=\" elementor-element elementor-element-09e0aef e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"09e0aef\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1f58e5c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"1f58e5c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-800940a elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"800940a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"453\" src=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/visuel-concours-eloquence.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-16066\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/visuel-concours-eloquence.webp 800w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/visuel-concours-eloquence-300x170.webp 300w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/visuel-concours-eloquence-768x435.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7ccfdbc e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7ccfdbc\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5b2b40b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5b2b40b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Concours d\u2019\u00e9loquence &amp; mobilisations citoyennes<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-01e30bc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"01e30bc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>La Fondation des Femmes organise \u00e9galement des concours d\u2019\u00e9loquence, temps forts permettant \u00e0 des jeunes femmes et hommes de prendre la parole sur l\u2019\u00e9galit\u00e9, les violences, le sexisme et les droits des femmes. Ces \u00e9v\u00e9nements s\u2019inscrivent dans une dynamique plus large de mobilisation autour du 8 mars et du 25 novembre, avec des rassemblements, prises de parole publiques, tribunes et actions communes avec des collectifs f\u00e9ministes.\u200b<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a77f6e4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a77f6e4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-677c50b e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"677c50b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5bf6c34 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5bf6c34\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><span class=\"highlight-jaune\">Former<\/span> et outiller le grand public<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-89a37e4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"89a37e4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-31c3889 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"31c3889\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"946\" src=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/2020-stand-up.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-16397\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/2020-stand-up.webp 800w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/2020-stand-up-254x300.webp 254w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/2020-stand-up-768x908.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-50098e8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"50098e8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3f383f7 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3f383f7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-be1e15f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"be1e15f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Stand-up<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d2cff66 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d2cff66\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">R\u00e9agir face au harc\u00e8lement de rue<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a72a206 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a72a206\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Le programme Stand Up, d\u00e9velopp\u00e9 avec L\u2019Or\u00e9al Paris et Right To Be, vise \u00e0 former le plus grand nombre \u00e0 r\u00e9agir face au harc\u00e8lement dans l\u2019espace public. En une heure, cette formation gratuite apprend les 5D (Distraire, D\u00e9l\u00e9guer, Documenter, Diriger, Dialoguer) pour intervenir en s\u00e9curit\u00e9, que l\u2019on soit t\u00e9moin ou victime.\u200b<br \/>En 2024, 17 374 personnes ont \u00e9t\u00e9 form\u00e9es en ligne, en pr\u00e9sentiel ou via des formats courts, portant \u00e0 plus de 69 000 le nombre total de personnes form\u00e9es depuis 2020.\u200b<br \/>Une nouvelle formation compl\u00e9mentaire (\u00ab Boussole \u00bb) viendra enrichir prochainement cet outillage, pour aider les femmes \u00e0 s\u2019orienter dans les dispositifs existants (droits, sant\u00e9, violences, emploi).<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-be86ca9 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"be86ca9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4a6991f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4a6991f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0863c2f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"0863c2f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4e92d32 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4e92d32\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Podcasts<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a2947ed elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a2947ed\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Donner la parole aux femmes<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6ba56e5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6ba56e5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>La Fondation des Femmes produit et diffuse plusieurs s\u00e9ries de podcasts pour faire entendre les voix des femmes, raconter leurs histoires et interroger les normes :<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5236dc2 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5236dc2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1976910 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"1976910\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/podcast.ausha.co\/ecoutez-nous-bien\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">\u00c9coutez-nous bien<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-05fc8b5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"05fc8b5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/podcast.ausha.co\/regarde-moi-bien\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Regarde-moi bien<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-246834c elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"246834c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/podcast.ausha.co\/fete-des-merveilleuses\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">F\u00eate des Merveilleuses<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e21e9ac elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e21e9ac\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Ces formats audio permettent de sensibiliser un public large, notamment les plus jeunes et les personnes \u00e9loign\u00e9es des formats militants classiques.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c135cbe elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"c135cbe\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"699\" src=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/former-podcasts.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-16064\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/former-podcasts.webp 700w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/former-podcasts-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/former-podcasts-150x150.webp 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c92967d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c92967d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e74e5b6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e74e5b6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8d4bbd6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"8d4bbd6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ae11203 text-pretty elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ae11203\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><span class=\"highlight-vert\">Transformer<\/span> la loi et les politiques publiques<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e3fbda7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e3fbda7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\u00c0 l\u2019\u00e9chelle soci\u00e9tale, la Force Juridique m\u00e8ne des actions de plaidoyer et des contentieux strat\u00e9giques pour faire \u00e9voluer la jurisprudence et les lois en faveur des droits des femmes.\u200b<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-08b4238 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"08b4238\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c278d3c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c278d3c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Contentieux strat\u00e9giques et grandes causes<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1a92d14 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1a92d14\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>La Force Juridique porte ou soutient des contentieux embl\u00e9matiques : affaires de violences sexuelles, industrie pornographique, soumission chimique, viol conjugal, etc., afin de cr\u00e9er des pr\u00e9c\u00e9dents et de mieux prot\u00e9ger les victimes. Ces actions contribuent \u00e0 faire \u00e9voluer l\u2019interpr\u00e9tation du droit p\u00e9nal, du droit de la famille ou encore du droit du travail en mati\u00e8re de violences et de discriminations.\u200b<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-67a5dd8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"67a5dd8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e7edfa5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e7edfa5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Plaidoyer aupr\u00e8s des institutions<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b46df75 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b46df75\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>La Force Juridique conduit \u00e9galement des actions de plaidoyer aupr\u00e8s des institutions pour promouvoir des r\u00e9formes l\u00e9gislatives essentielles, parmi lesquelles :<\/p><ul role=\"list\"><li>La constitutionnalisation de l\u2019IVG, obtenue en mars 2024 apr\u00e8s deux ans de mobilisation aux c\u00f4t\u00e9s d\u2019autres organisations f\u00e9ministes.\u200b<\/li><li>Une meilleure r\u00e9gulation de l\u2019espace num\u00e9rique pour prot\u00e9ger les femmes contre les violences en ligne (cyberharc\u00e8lement, revenge porn, campagnes de haine).\u200b<\/li><li>Le renforcement des moyens publics pour lutter contre les violences et soutenir les associations f\u00e9ministes.\u200b<\/li><\/ul><p><br \/>L\u2019int\u00e9gration des enjeux \u00e9conomiques (pensions alimentaires, co\u00fbt du divorce, pr\u00e9carit\u00e9 des m\u00e8res isol\u00e9es) dans les politiques publiques d\u2019\u00e9galit\u00e9.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-91fb2cf e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"91fb2cf\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ef9c2bb elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ef9c2bb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Un think tank juridique f\u00e9ministe<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9f041c7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9f041c7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>La Force Juridique constitue aussi la dimension think tank juridique f\u00e9ministe de la Fondation. Son ambition est de construire une doctrine f\u00e9ministe du droit, en articulant expertise juridique, analyse f\u00e9ministe et action publique : guides pratiques (comme \u00ab Sant\u00e9 gyn\u00e9cologique : mes droits, mes choix \u00bb), articles sp\u00e9cialis\u00e9s, notes de position, conf\u00e9rences, webinaires.\u200b<br \/>En ce sens, la Force Juridique ne se limite pas \u00e0 accompagner ou d\u00e9fendre : elle participe activement \u00e0 transformer le droit pour en faire un outil d\u2019\u00e9galit\u00e9 r\u00e9elle.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c2e462 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"5c2e462\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9e7bed6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"9e7bed6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c194eaf elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c194eaf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">La cit\u00e9 <span class=\"highlight-jaune\">audacieuse<\/span><\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-03ec168 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"03ec168\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Un tiers-lieu pour se mobiliser<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d6694a9 lien-hypertexte elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d6694a9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Inaugur\u00e9e en 2020 au c\u0153ur de Paris, la Cit\u00e9 Audacieuse est le premier lieu d\u00e9di\u00e9 au rayonnement des droits des femmes en France. Pens\u00e9e comme un tiers-lieu f\u00e9ministe, elle accueille des associations, des porteur\u00b7ses de projets, des \u00e9v\u00e8nements, un caf\u00e9 associatif et un studio de podcast, et constitue un v\u00e9ritable point de ralliement pour toutes celles et ceux qui veulent agir pour l\u2019\u00e9galit\u00e9.\u200b<br \/>En 2024, la Cit\u00e9 Audacieuse a accueilli 256 \u00e9v\u00e9nements sur les droits des femmes et sensibilis\u00e9 plus de 8 000 personnes, avec une fr\u00e9quentation en hausse de 76,5% par rapport \u00e0 2023. Elle a \u00e9galement \u00e9t\u00e9 labellis\u00e9e Lieu totem de l\u2019\u00e9galit\u00e9 dans le cadre des Jeux Olympiques et Paralympiques de Paris 2024.\u200b<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2343c3a elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"2343c3a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/citeaudacieuse.fr\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Visiter la Cit\u00e9 Audacieuse<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-302a3dc elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"302a3dc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1766\" height=\"1602\" src=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/cite-audacieuse.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-16065\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/cite-audacieuse.webp 1766w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/cite-audacieuse-300x272.webp 300w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/cite-audacieuse-1024x929.webp 1024w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/cite-audacieuse-768x697.webp 768w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/cite-audacieuse-1536x1393.webp 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1766px) 100vw, 1766px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3d73c77 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3d73c77\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59d3544 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"59d3544\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8c6906d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8c6906d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Questions fr\u00e9quentes<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aaf6f10 elementor-widget elementor-widget-n-accordion\" data-id=\"aaf6f10\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;default_state&quot;:&q